'''Squib Reclamation''' was a [[Squib/Legends|Squib]]-owned corporation that specialized in collecting galactic garbage.<ref name="DB Squib">{{DB|species|squib|Squib}}.</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Squib Reclamation is mentioned in the Squib [[Databank (original)|Databank]] article on the official ''Star Wars'' website. The entry does not specify the relationship between the company and the similarly named [[Squib Reclamation Fleet]].<ref name="DB Squib" />

